      <div class="svc"><div class="svc-top"><span class="svc-num">05</span><div class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg></div></div><div class="svc-title">Social Media Auto-Posting</div><div class="svc-tagline">Your brand · Always present</div><p class="svc-desc">AI-drafted content, one-click approval, automated scheduling across LinkedIn and Twitter — daily, without you.</p><div class="svc-stack">LinkedIn API · Twitter · Claude AI</div></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="svc-top"><span class="svc-num">06</span><div class="ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M4.93 4.93a10 10 0 0 0 0 14.14"/></svg></div></div><div class="svc-title">AI Support Desk</div><div class="svc-tagline">Answers in seconds · Always on</div><p class="svc-desc">Custom AI trained on your business, handling queries, qualifying leads, and escalating only what needs a human.</p><div class="svc-stack">Claude · GPT · Custom RAG</div></div>
