<section class="section" id="pricing">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="pricing-hd"><div class="ey rev" style="justify-content:center">Pricing</div><h2 class="h2 rev d1" style="text-align:center">Simple pricing.<br><em>Serious results.</em></h2><p class="sub rev d2" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto">No surprise invoices. No retainer traps. Pick what fits.</p></div>
    <div class="pgrid">
      <div class="pcard rev d1"><div class="p-tier">Starter</div><div class="p-price"><sup>$</sup>999</div><div class="p-period">one-time project</div><div class="p-tagline">First automation · done right</div><div class="p-div"></div><p class="p-desc">For businesses automating their first process or producing their first AI video.</p><ul class="p-feats"><li>1 custom n8n workflow</li><li>Up to 5 nodes / integrations</li><li>Error handling &amp; retries</li><li>1 AI avatar video (3 min)</li><li>2 weeks post-launch support</li><li>Full workflow documentation</li></ul><a href="#contact" class="p-btn pb-gh">Get started</a></div>
      <div class="pcard feat rev d2"><div class="p-badge">Most popular</div><div class="p-tier">Growth</div><div class="p-price"><sup>$</sup>2,499</div><div class="p-period">per month retainer</div><div class="p-tagline">Automation as a growth engine</div><div class="p-div"></div><p class="p-desc">For businesses serious about automation as strategy — ongoing build, optimise, expand.</p><ul class="p-feats"><li>Up to 4 workflows / month</li><li>Lead generation pipeline</li><li>4 AI videos / month</li><li>WhatsApp automation</li><li>Social auto-posting pipeline</li><li>Monthly performance review</li><li>Priority support</li></ul><a href="#contact" class="p-btn pb-lt">Book a strategy call</a></div>
      <div class="pcard rev d3"><div class="p-tier">Enterprise</div><div class="p-price" style="font-size:36px;letter-spacing:-1px">Custom</div><div class="p-period">bespoke engagement</div><div class="p-tagline">Automation embedded end-to-end</div><div class="p-div"></div><p class="p-desc">For companies embedding automation into every layer of their operation.</p><ul class="p-feats"><li>Unlimited workflows</li><li>Dedicated architect</li><li>Full AI video suite</li><li>Custom AI support desk</li><li>Staff training &amp; handover</li><li>SLA &amp; monitoring</li><li>Multi-region compliance</li></ul><a href="#contact" class="p-btn pb-dk">Let's talk</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section faq-bg" id="faq">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="faq-layout">
      <div><div class="ey rev"><span class="ey-bar"></span>FAQ</div><h2 class="h2 rev d1">Questions worth<br>asking before<br><em>you reach out.</em></h2><p class="sub rev d2" style="margin-top:14px">If it's not here — that's what the strategy call is for.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-list rev d1">
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Do I need technical knowledge to use the automations?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">No. We build workflows that run without your technical involvement. We document everything clearly, train your team, and make sure you can monitor — and pause — any automation without touching code.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What makes n8n better than Zapier or Make?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">n8n is self-hosted — you own your data and pay no per-task fees as you scale. It's significantly more powerful for complex, conditional workflows. We'll recommend the right tool for your situation — Zapier and Make have their place too.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How long does it take to build and deploy a workflow?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">Simple workflows: 3–5 days. Complex multi-step pipelines: 2–3 weeks. AI video production: 24–72 hours per video. We'll give a precise timeline after discovery.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What if a workflow breaks after handover?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">Every workflow includes error handling, automatic retries, and alert notifications. We monitor for 2 weeks post-launch. Growth plan clients have ongoing support — we fix issues same day.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Are AI videos good enough for professional use?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">With HeyGen and Sync.so — yes, for demos, onboarding, training, and social content. We're honest about where a human presenter is still better, and we'll tell you before you spend a penny.</div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="faq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Do you work with clients outside Pakistan?</span><span class="faq-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 3v10M3 8h10"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a">Yes — most clients are in the UK, US, Europe, and the Middle East. We've been remote-first since 2013. Time zones, async communication, and global delivery are built into how we work.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

